 -- Ubuntu daily release <ps-jenkins@lists.canonical.com>  Mon, 17 Feb 2014 19:40:33 +0000

unity-scope-click (0.1+14.04.20140217.2-0ubuntu1) trusty; urgency=low

  [ Jussi Pakkanen ]
  * Minor fixes.
  * Order applications so that newest installed come first.
  * Rename categories as per the newest spec.
  * Remove double add.

 -- Ubuntu daily release <ps-jenkins@lists.canonical.com>  Mon, 17 Feb 2014 16:31:25 +0000

